{"word":"Barley","slug":"barley","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Barley</b> A product of Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=9&verse=31'>Exo 9:31</a><br/> A product of Palestine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=8&verse=8'>Deu 8:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=11&verse=13'>1Ch 11:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=41&verse=8'>Jer 41:8</a><br/> Fed to horses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=28'>1Ki 4:28</a><br/> Used in offerings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=5&verse=15'>Num 5:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=45&verse=15'>Eze 45:15</a><br/> Traffic in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=10'>2Ch 2:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=3&verse=2'>Hos 3:2</a><br/> Tribute in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=27&verse=5'>2Ch 27:5</a><br/> Priests estimated value of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=27&verse=16'>Lev 27:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=7&verse=1'>2Ki 7:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=6&verse=6'>Rev 6:6</a><br/> Absalom burns Joab's field of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=14&verse=30'>2Sa 14:30</a><br/> Loaves of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=9'>Joh 6:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=13'>Joh 6:13</a>"}]}